name: Tez Dizpenser ⁄ Sun ⁄ SYSTEMA SOLARIS ⁄ #10
description: Meet the Sun. SYSTEMA SOLARIS is a series of 10 works that captures the sheer beauty and size of our solar system. Each unique 1 of 1 Tez Dizpenser showcases that celestial body's scale, moon(s), rings, color and its distant view of the sun. Join me on this space-bound voyage. Collect them all! 〔 Diameter: 865,370 mi 〕〔 Average Temperature: 9,941°F 〕 Twitter: @cmilburndesign – Clubhouse: @codestrong
